usage: mdchksum [-h?l] [-f] file

  -h, -? : show this message
  -f     : automatically fix the checksum
  -l     : display license information
  file   : name of file to check

The program assumes the file specified is a valid
Sega Genesis / Mega Drive rom in BIN / RAW format;
currently no checking is done to verify this.
Do not try to fix the checksum on arbitrary files,
as this will almost certainly cause problems.
